doc.previous: WSJ is The Wall Street Journal s luxury lifestyle magazine Its coverage spans art fashion entertainment design food architecture travel and more Kristina O Neill is Editor in Chief and Anthony Cenname is Publisher
doc.after: Launched as a quarterly in 2008 the magazine grew to 12 issues a year for 2014 39 The magazine is distributed within the U S Weekend Edition of The Wall Street Journal newspaper average paid print circulation is 2 2 million the European and Asian editions and is available on WSJ com Each issue is also available throughout the month in The Wall Street Journal s iPad app
